16
00:01:00,201 --> 00:01:08,207
[SPEAKER_04]: We're going to give you five minutes to set out your vision about how you see the job as UN Secretary General and how you're going to do it.

17
00:01:08,587 --> 00:01:11,129
[SPEAKER_04]: Five minutes and I will give you a four minute warning.

18
00:01:11,718 --> 00:01:12,179
[SPEAKER_02]: Very good.

19
