[SPEAKER_02]: Well, thank you, thank you.

20
00:01:13,900 --> 00:01:30,936
[SPEAKER_02]: It's great to be here, this historic place, and to see that so many are equally concerned and supportive of the United Nations and a multilateral answer to the problems of the day.

21
00:01:32,198 --> 00:01:33,979
[SPEAKER_02]: This next election,

22
00:01:35,103 --> 00:01:49,409
[SPEAKER_02]: of the Secretary General of the United Nations, in my opinion, might arguably be the most consequential one in the history of the organization.

23
00:01:49,549 --> 00:01:51,370
[SPEAKER_02]: And I believe this because

24
