[SPEAKER_02]: global crisis of different natures.

26
00:02:11,103 --> 00:02:37,218
[SPEAKER_02]: But what is especially worrying this time and for this particular selection process is that we see a fundamental, I would say, crisis of confidence in the United Nations, in the possibility and in the ability of the United Nations to be a factor that would be able to influence

