55
00:06:56,640 --> 00:06:58,662
[SPEAKER_02]: Sustainable development goals.

56
00:06:58,902 --> 00:07:03,367
[SPEAKER_02]: When we look at that, and mind you, 2030 is around the corner.

57
00:07:03,507 --> 00:07:05,469
[SPEAKER_04]: It's a rules-based order in your five minutes are up.

58
00:07:05,689 --> 00:07:06,009
[SPEAKER_04]: Thank you.

59
00:07:14,616 --> 00:07:16,497
