66
00:07:40,490 --> 00:07:42,231
[SPEAKER_04]: What, the need for a woman or?

67
00:07:42,251 --> 00:07:43,952
[SPEAKER_02]: The issue of man or woman.

68
00:07:44,802 --> 00:07:46,803
[SPEAKER_02]: the issue of a man or a woman.

69
00:07:47,944 --> 00:07:57,850
[SPEAKER_02]: When we are selecting Secretary General, we are selecting a person, the best person for the job, the best person for the job.

70
00:08:01,813 --> 00:08:09,718
[SPEAKER_02]: And to be the best person, the best person to incarnate this crucial function,

