00:17:17,535 --> 00:17:18,375
[SPEAKER_02]: It's an evidence.

164
00:17:18,935 --> 00:17:19,656
[SPEAKER_02]: It's an evidence.

165
00:17:19,956 --> 00:17:35,419
[SPEAKER_02]: But this is why I say that it is in the area of international peace and security there is a moral and statutory obligation for the Secretary General to assume these roles.

166
